<h1>The Abjad <_LeafDurationInterface> class</h1> 
<subsection>

<p>
The Abjad <_LeafDurationInterface> class manages note, rest, chord and skip duration.
</p>

</subsection>

<interface>
<attributes>
   <local> multiplied
   <local> multiplier
   <inherited> prolated
   <inherited> prolation
   <inherited> prolations
   <local> written
</attributes>
<methods>
   <local> rewrite
</methods>
</interface>

<section> Attributes

<subsection>

<abjad>
   abjad> measure = Measure((4, 4), [ ])
   abjad> measure.append(FixedDurationTuplet((2, 4), Note(0, (1, 4)) * 3))
   abjad> measure.append(FixedDurationTuplet((2, 4), Note(0, (1, 4)) * 3))
   abjad> note = measure.leaves[0]
   abjad> show(measure)
</abjad>

</subsection>

<definition>
<header>
   <local> multiplier
   <p>Read / write attribute defined here.</p>
   <p>Optional LilyPond multiplier to attached leaf.</p>
   <p>Returns Abjad <Rational>.</p>
   <p>Accepts Abjad <duration token>, <code>None</code>.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.multiplier is None
      True
   </abjad>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.multiplier = (1, 2)
      abjad> print(note.format)
      c'4 * 1/2
   </abjad>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.multiplier = None
      abjad> note.duration.multiplier is None
      True
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

<definition>
<header>
   <inherited> preprolated
   <p>Read-only attribute inherited from <_DurationInterface>.</p>
   <p>Returns Abjad <Rational>.</p>
   <p>Represents leaf duration prior to consideration of any tuplet or measure scaling.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.preprolated
      Rational(1, 4) 
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

<definition>
<header>
   <inherited> prolated
   <p>Read-only attribute inherited from <_DurationInterface>.</p>
   <p>Returns Abjad <Rational>.</p>
   <p>Represents scaled leaf duration accounting for any tuplet or measure scaling.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.prolated
      Rational(1, 6) 
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

<definition>
<header>
   <inherited> prolation
   <p>Read-only attribute inherited from <_DurationInterface>.</p>
   <p>Returns Abjad <Rational>.</p>
   <p>Represents scaling factor donated by all tuplets and measures enclosing leaf.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.prolation
      Rational(2, 3)
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

<definition>
<header>
   <local> written
   <p>Read / write attribute defined here.</p>
   <p>Returns Abjad <Rational>.</p>
   <p>Accepts Abjad <duration token>.</p>
   <p>Represents the written, face value of leaf without consideration of LilyPond multipliers or tuplet or mesaure scaling.</p>
   <p>Abjad written duration corresponds most closely to notional intuition of duration.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.written
      Rational(1, 4)
   </abjad>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.written = (3, 8)
      abjad> note
      Note(c', 4.)
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

<section> Methods

<definition>
<header>
   <local> rewrite
   <p>rewrite(<i>arg</i>)</p>
   <p>Public method defined here.</p>
   <p>Changes written duration of leaf to arg while leaving preprolated duration of leaf the same through multiplier adjustment.</p>
</header>
<body>
   <abjad>
      abjad> note.duration.written = (1, 4)
      abjad> note.duration.rewrite((1, 16))
      abjad> note.duration.written
      Rational(1, 16)
      abjad> note.duration.multiplier
      Rational(4, 1)
   </abjad>
</body>
</definition>

